title: The Converse Chuck Taylor All Star II
description:
Ready for more. Available now in select countries.

The Chuck II features a Lunarlon Sockliner for more cushioning and support, super soft Micro-Suede Lining, a Padded Non-Slip Tongue for 360 degree comfort around the ankle and instep, and Premium Canvas for high quality touch and texture.
